lead_paragraph: Carlos Gomez hit a towering three-run homer in the eighth inning and the AL-leading Texas Rangers beat the Milwaukee Brewers 8-5 on Wednesday night for their MLB-best 49th come-from-behind victory.

headline.print_headline: Gomez Homers in 8th, Rangers Rally Again to Beat Brewers 8-5
